title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 14-4.32 - Definition of person
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 14-4.32 - Definition of person

State Regulations
A person, as used by this Subpart, is an individual, firm, estate, partnership, company, corporation, trustee, association, or any public or private entity. Notes
